language Essence 1.3

given g: int(1..)
given s: int(1..)
given w: int(1..)
letting n be g * s
find schedule: matrix indexed by [int(1..w)] of partition (numParts g, partSize s) from int(1..n)
such that
    and([and([and([p1 < p2 -> !(together({p1, p2}, schedule[w1]) /\ together({p1, p2}, schedule[w2]))
                       | p1 : int(1..n), p2 : int(1..n)])
                  | w2 : int(w1 + 1..w)])
             | w1 : int(1..w)])

